project.caption: This is a web application that I created in 2019 for Ebla Private university students in Aleppo.
project.description: This is a web application that I created in 2019 for Ebla Private university students in Aleppo, which is designed in a simple and easy-to-use manner to help university students browse and download lectures at any time they want. I also feel proud that I offer this service to my colleagues completely free of charge.
